  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This multicenter, prospective, observational cohort study will assess bone differences in
      women and men with type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM) with and without fragility fractures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Cross-sectional evaluation of clinical, biochemical and microstructural measures of bone in
      patients with type 2 diabetes and age-matched healthy controls. Longitudinal assessment of
      clinical, biochemical and microstructural measures of bone in study participants without
      prevalent fragility fractures.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
